creator: Eugene Field
description:
LibriVox recording of With Two Spoons For Two Spoons by Eugene Field.
Read in English by AnnaMarie Tokas; Ann Boulais; Bruce Kachuk; Doug Fajardo; fshort; Greg Giordano; Lee Ann Howlett; MaryAnn; Maria Kasper
Librivox volunteers bring you nine readings of With Two Spoons For Two Spoons, by Eugene Field. This was the weekly poem for the week of December 7, 2014. Summary by Ann Boulais
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
